Do you just wake up in the
morning thinking about them

00:21:59.220 --> 00:22:01.094
or as you're just walking
down the street you

00:22:01.094 --> 00:22:04.155
see things that spike interest?

00:22:04.155 --> 00:22:06.160
LUBOC AZRIA: Lisa, I
