But it used to be were
Alexander the Great came.

00:33:44.410 --> 00:33:46.467
That country used
to rule the world.

00:34:02.500 --> 00:34:04.320
And again, they're
just effortless pieces.

00:34:04.320 --> 00:34:05.680
You just put them on and go.

