have everything open.

00:34:34.260 --> 00:34:39.670
Down the runway, you need to get
that wow feeling for editors.

00:34:39.670 --> 00:34:42.010
So you don't line the
dresses most of the time.

00:34:42.010 --> 00:34:45.610
And you leave things a
little bit more open.

00:34:45.610 --> 00:34:52.960
But in real life,
it's much more safe.

00:34:52.960 --> 00:34:53.460
Yeah.

