This collection is so
interesting because

00:35:09.980 --> 00:35:13.570
from the beginning, from
the first piece to the time

00:35:13.570 --> 00:35:17.330
that it actually makes it to the
store, I see it like 30 times.

00:35:17.330 --> 00:35:19.270
And I know when
something is good is

00:35:19.270 --> 00:35:21.550
when I'm not tired of it.

00:35:21.550 --> 00:35:25.610
Like, I'm still excited to
go then and actually wear it.

00:35:25.610 --> 00:35:28.055
And that to me is when the
collection really resonates.

