00:40:45.790 --> 00:40:48.800
And just analyzing it, so you're
not just seeing the clothes

00:40:48.800 --> 00:40:51.610
and how beautiful they
are, but the contrast.

00:40:51.610 --> 00:40:54.490
The belt, the lines, how
